<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>Flight Tracker</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Flight Tracker</h1>
  </header>

  <main>
		<p>Track flights in real-time, search airports, and save flights to your personal watchlist.</p>

		<section>
			<h2>Airport Search</h2>
			<p>Find flights near any airport</p>
			<p>Search for airports by ICAO code to see live flights in the area with real-time data from OpenSky Network.</p>
			<a href="/airportQuery">Search Airports</a>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>My Watchlist</h2>
			<p>Track your saved flights</p>
			<p>View and manage flights you've saved. Add notes, set priorities, and stay organized.</p>
			<a href="/saved">View Watchlist</a>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Add Flight</h2>
			<p>Manually add to watchlist</p>
			<p>Know a flight number? Add it directly to your watchlist with custom notes and priority.</p>
			<a href="/saved/add">Add Flight</a>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>How it works</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>Search — Find airports and view live flights</li>
				<li>Track — Get detailed flight information</li>
				<li>Save — Add flights to your watchlist</li>
				<li>Organize — Set priorities and add notes</li>
			</ol>
		</section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>Flight data powered by OpenSky Network & AviationStack</p>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>